This project comprise of the assignment given by FullThrottle Labs.
Following is the step by step procedure to get the desired result.
Create a virtaul environment in the command prompt and install Django.
Then comes creation of project and app. Followed by including app name in settings.py
Model is then created according to the situation like I was given for user and date and timee
The model is migrated to SQLlite or any other type of database followed by dataloading.
Then Django REST Framework JSON API is installes and mentioned in settings.py
After that naother script was made sterlizer.py.
Then comes changes in views.py and urls.py.
https://howtojsonapi.com/django.html can be followed for the tutorial.
It is the simpleast among all.